{"tid":996473,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"因為連登，我個人改變左好多","createTime":"2019-01-26T10:12:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T02:01:45.000Z","uid":224836,"like":136,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a053f767e067da29c52836f4cee1033f2a8816f5","tid":996473,"uid":224836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:12:29.000Z","msg":"以前好少上連登 個人正正常常<br />\n社交無咩問題 好多朋友都鍾意同我玩<br />\n前幾年開始多左上呢個討論區 留意連登啲帖同埋留言<br />\n不知不覺間連登果種好偏激既價值觀同諗法就套落左我身上<br />\n我本身自己都反共同埋覺得環保撚啲走塑批鬥好有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以都幾buy普遍連登仔既logic <br />\n自己都會私下係社交網站開po屌鳩呢樣果樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗住可以發洩同埋改變下身邊既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而且上得連登多 個人都變得口沒遮攔 講野好嘴賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n慢慢咁身邊既人都開始唔太想理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一部分覺得我諗野太偏激<br />\n一部分就覺得我成日批鬥人好討厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一部分就覺得我成個連登仔咁既性格好反鹿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得上左連登之後 個人又變得負面左 價值觀同埋思想都比較偏激左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 導致身邊啲人慢慢唔鍾意自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都會慢慢改善下自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同埋勸下大家真係上連登勿認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"778ab4946f94530f20b89f1ba64204eb28978b8c","tid":996473,"uid":40470,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:13:59.000Z","msg":"你上網同人講身高185<br />\n<br />\n月入80k?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n現實身高165<br />\n<br />\n月入13k<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf170eb86661e1e0dba9afe7354d72371a53655","tid":996473,"uid":80419,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:15:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n瀨得就瀨"},{"pid":"060a5063bf92f3811e03a2f0a92628be09320a75","tid":996473,"uid":230890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:16:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"834599157307d8036e43370df4fc9e31948a81b7","tid":996473,"uid":224836,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6cf170eb86661e1e0dba9afe7354d72371a53655","tid":996473,"uid":80419,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:15:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n瀨得就瀨"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:17:31.000Z","msg":"係我啲朋友同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  因為佢地都知我有上連登呢個習慣"},{"pid":"b5ee2c3bae8cfb7fbd647a9ae2ab6b7943c98990","tid":996473,"uid":230890,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:17:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"645734e33402e89a18672ee75689680689eaf943","tid":996473,"uid":224836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"778ab4946f94530f20b89f1ba64204eb28978b8c","tid":996473,"uid":40470,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:13:59.000Z","msg":"你上網同人講身高185<br />\n<br />\n月入80k?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n現實身高165<br />\n<br />\n月入13k<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:17:58.000Z","msg":"無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61db87b6da4f3ffe13a4f3eb4544d1792563c3ae","tid":996473,"uid":191988,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a053f767e067da29